summary: A player owned farmhouse that contains bookshelves, mannequins, skill books and more.
descriptionHtml:
UPDATED 2/26/12 

-Added a pond on the east side of the property with salmon and a fisherman
-Fixed the floating stone walls
-Fixed the floating books in the living room bookshelf
-Added more crops & a horse stable
-Fixed the landscape up a bit and added a variety of trees

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This mod adds a farmhouse east of Rorikstead. The farm contains a horse, a dog, cows, chickens, goats, a vegetable & herb garden, archery targets, a smithing forge with a table full of ingots for training, a grindstone, workbench, tanning rack.

The inside of the house has 2 mannequins, 4 bookshelves, an alchemy & enchanting table, several weapon racks/glass cases, a bookshelf full of spell books in the upstairs bedroom, and a cooking range.
author: SqueakyDoggy
